* Version 0.6.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.5.4 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.5.3 (2015-05-31)
I: Minor Ansible role 'state' improvement

* Version 0.5.2 (2014-12-14)
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.5.1 (2014-09-11)
I: Change license from 'GPLv2' to 'Simplified BSD License'

* Version 0.5.0 (2014-08-22)
F: Add support for OS family 'FreeBSD'

* Version 0.4.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.3.1 (2014-08-14)
I: Improve conditional statements

* Version 0.3.0 (2014-07-26)
F: Add empty 'motd' template

* Version 0.2.1 (2014-06-15)
I: Modify 'robomon' logo

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-05-25)
I: Improve environment color option

* Version 0.1.1 (2014-04-17)
B: Fix include statement

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-03-28)
F: Initial release
